snippet.title: Movie Burner Entertainment
snippet.description:
The Movie Burner Entertainment YouTube Channel hosts Movie News Live Monday to Thursday and a surprise Movie Review Live every Friday. Also, Keep an eye out for Trailer Reactions from the MBE team!!
